  <prompt>Add integration test invoking /narrate against running BFF. Verify response JSON shape (top-level fields: `tldr`, `channelNarratives`, `generatedUtc`) matches what existing `parseNotificationData` consumes. Compare against a frozen R3 sample at `notes/samples/narrate-response-r3.json` (capture it first if not present).</prompt>
  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. Integration testing of BFF /narrate response contract; freeze the R3 shape as golden sample.</role>
  <goal>Integration test exists asserting /narrate response shape matches `notes/samples/narrate-response-r3.json`. Test passes against task 031's playbook-dispatch implementation. Sample file captured + checked in if not already present.</goal>
